,Recommended,285330,35499133,Posted: 5 October,all,AmethystKacey,"I remember playing this when i was about 12 years old. And it hasn't changed!I have always loved playing RCT and it is a great simulation.I find a few of the beginner parks are really hard to achieve the objectives so dont feel too bad, Just skip and go back!There are some neat tricks to be found online as well, like renaming guests to people who made the game and they do different things.I really recommend this game to anyone who loves simulation games and likes spending hours building awesome theme parks!"
